  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Conjure Library SPELL 1</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">[Uncommon][Divination][Dynamic Heightening]</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Traditions arcane, occult</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Access worships Princess Luminace or zebra</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cast [two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Despite its name this spell does not actually conjure books—instead it creates a conduit between the caster and Princess Luminace's eternal library, allowing for a glimpse of unfathomable knowledge. This peek grants you one attempt to Recall Knowledge with a +4 circumstance bonus.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+1) The spell's duration extends by one round, allowing further Recall Knowledges to be made.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+1) Enlisting the aid of one of her luminaries, any critical failure made on an enhanced Recall Knowledge roll becomes a failure instead.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+1) Offering up your power, you are able to peek into less open areas of the library, removing any penalty for Uncommon knowledge.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-eefc0a39-7fff-b8b8-cdc6-d3e342be7409\">Heightened </strong>(+2) Offering up your power, you are able to peek into less open areas of the library, removing any penalty for Rare knowledge.</p>"
    },
